headline: PG&E Participates in First-Ever Autonomous Wildfire Suppression Demonstration in California
summary: Pacific Gas and Electric Company recently joined elite fire professionals, top state and federal officials, and senior leaders representing philanthropy, insurance providers, and other electric utilities for the first-ever autonomous wildfire suppression demonstration in California.
